    <h1 class="c-page-title">How to fix the WHO, according to an expert</h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">President Trump’s threat to take funding from the World Health Organization won’t change it. Here’s what might.</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
